responsibilities:
Acts as the representative for the Congresswoman to constituents and federal
agencies, primarily with the Department of Homeland Security and the Department
of State;

qualifications:
Ability to exercise discretion and independent judgment when fulfilling casework
responsibilities including respecting the privacy of constituents seeking
assistance;

responsibilities:
Work closely with the Scheduler to ensure that the Member's appointments are on time
and that the team is aware of the visitors' arrival; assisting with staffing of meetings as
